text: Salem Ould Habib (born 6 April 1964) is a Mauritanian freestyle wrestler. Habib competed for Mauritania at the 1988 Summer Olympics in the 74 kg freestyle wrestling event, he lost both opening group matches so didn't advance to the next round. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic wrestlers of Mauritania Category:Wrestlers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Mauritanian male sport wrestlers
